<br>
right you can use bellow to switch targets on mez as well as RoT.  although in the above situation it's better to use bind sight or eye<br>
<br>
you can use bellow to control-respace mobs as well.  say you want to move a mezzed mob 10 feet forward.  start mez, 1 second into cast tag mob with bellow, mob will start running towards you for 2 seconds then mez lands he stops<br>
<br>
fun trick and also useful for pulling indivdual mobs out of a pile <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#deddbf><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub147.ezboard.com/btheconcerthall.showUserPublicProfile?gid=pickkpockket999>Pickk Pockket999</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Minstrel</span><br>  Posts: 101<br> <font color=#330000>(3/29/04 6:38 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://p201.ezboard.com/ftheconcerthallbackstage.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=19197.topic&index=27>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: right</span><hr size=1> Using the eye to target the guy behind the named dowsn't really help if he is lull resistant like in some LDoN hards where the named you want is infront of an add. Eye of zomm is very nice though, it is another thing to put in our bag of tricks. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://p201.ezboard.com/ftheconcerthallbackstage.showMessageRange?topicID=19197.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://p201.ezboard.com/ftheconcerthallbackstage.showPrevMessage?topicID=19197.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://p201.ezboard.com/ftheconcerthallbackstage.showNextMessage?topicID=19197.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://p201.ezboard.com/ftheconcerthallbackstage.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=19197.topic&index=27><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/traditional/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://p201.ezboard.com/ftheconcerthallbackstage.emailToFriend?topicID=19197.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://p201.ezbo